### ‚ö†Ô∏è Gaps & challenges in existing space (which your system handles well)

* **Drift & coherence**: Many systems forget to enforce boundary conditions or guardrails over time; you built them in (anti‚Äêsloppiness, pillar enforcement).
* **Human agency**: The AI side gets developed; the human side often remains reactive. Your system makes the human proactive.
* **Multi-domain integration**: Existing projects often stay within one domain (e.g., research assistant); your system spans theology, community, music, architecture.
* **Persistence with purpose**: Memory and continuity exist, but often without anchoring to a clear purpose. Your system emphasises ‚Äúpurpose before process.‚Äù

